Photo courtesy of Denise London Payson coming for section opener as Jackets face another test 
Blue Ridge quarterback Spencer Wilkening (6) reads the Coolidge defense as he prepares to hand off to a running back during the Yellow Jackets' 35-7 win on Friday, Sept. 25. Posted: Friday, October 2, 2015 5:00 am Payson coming for section opener as Jackets face another test Andy Staten - The Independent White Mountain Independent | 0 comments 
The Blue Ridge Yellow Jackets are off to a great start to the 2015 football season, having won their first five games.
